attributes.mlflow.spanInputs: {"prompt": "Create IOS XR telemetry configuration to stream BFD data to 192.0.2.100 port 57000 using grpc tls."}
attributes.mlflow.spanOutputs:
"telemetry model-driven
 sensor-group BFD-STATE
  sensor-path Cisco-IOS-XR-bundlemgr-oper:bundle-information/bundle-briefs/bundle-brief/bundle-brief-item/bfd-config
 !
 destination-group DG-GRPC
  address-family ipv4
   destination 192.0.2.100
    port 57000
    encoding self-describing-gpb
    protocol grpc no-tls
 !
 subscription SUB-BFD
  sensor-group-id BFD-STATE sample-interval 30000
  destination-group-id DG-GRPC
 !"
